{"tid":625544,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣秘方小鍋米線 湯底明火熬足6小時","createTime":"2018-04-11T14:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T16:01:57.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"16c2e41d0a7aa506ae4ceb78da2265561dda1c02","tid":625544,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:03:16.000Z","msg":"荃灣美食多眾所周知，但是都集中在同一條街。這次發掘了一家在旺區以外的米線店，店家招牌的 小鍋米線 是師傅親自在雲南麗江學師，熬足6小時而成，絕對地道～<br />\n<br />\n小鍋米線（酸辣／麻辣）$25<br />\n小鍋米線 湯底每日新鮮用30磅豬骨、雞、金華火腿等明火熬足6小時精製而成，賣完要等第二日才可以再品嚐。有別於其他米線店，用明火熬煮湯底確實十分罕有，而且每碗均是以湯頭獨立煮，非常用心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/poortravellers.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/03.jpg?resize=768%2C512\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fpoortravellers.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F03.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C512&h=94be5a45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n米線粗幼、軟硬適中，亦不會煮得太碎。辣度由不辣、不酸到BB辣至勁辣均可選擇，順應不同口味。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://i2.wp.com/poortravellers.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/02.jpg?resize=768%2C512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fpoortravellers.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F02.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C512&d=MXqbSAbZDu%2FemF4bcT8PWZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ad852efc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i2.wp.com/poortravellers.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/02.jpg?resize=768%2C512</a><br />\n<br />\n腩肉是小店的招牌配料，不少客人專程是一試再試就是為了腩肉。跟外面米線店不同，這裡的腩肉是比較瘦，切得也較為幼身，但是卻很入味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/poortravellers.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/07-1.jpg?resize=768%2C512\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fpoortravellers.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F07-1.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C512&h=2d17af68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最推介的小食！墨魚頭口感爽、彈，夠新鮮；調味酸酸辣辣，甚為開胃。店家的醬汁是自己的配方，這碟的配汁用上蒜頭，但能做到蒜香而不口臭～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/poortravellers.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/08-1.jpg?resize=768%2C512\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fpoortravellers.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F08-1.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C512&h=3d403f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抵食之選，平均$4一件。春卷皮用上網狀，炸得剛好，完全不會覺得油膩，放久了仍然保留脆身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/poortravellers.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/09-1.jpg?resize=768%2C512\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fpoortravellers.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F09-1.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C512&h=55b3f0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喜歡蒜香的不可以錯過。滿滿的五花肉片上舖滿香蒜，並灑上白芝麻，香氣十足。"},{"pid":"7e732f960cbcdde10597dcbe6e4772f1c315cf35","tid":625544,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:04:09.000Z","msg":"雲家小鍋米線<br />\n地址：荃灣沙咀道328號寶石樓地下G01舖（聖芳濟中學對面）<br />\n電話：2439 5767<br />\n營業時間：11:00-23:00"},{"pid":"69946e5edb651654e2651f194f5151bd4ad9dcf2","tid":625544,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ipick.com/htpic/59c20bbbbccb9186f2643598d7fa776f/2000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fipick.com%2Fhtpic%2F59c20bbbbccb9186f2643598d7fa776f%2F2000&h=7c16e2c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9fe33d89f39f69755ee09b8e3bcb7d64675fbcd","tid":625544,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3be49979f674a78cc8550540bf6e4210270871","tid":625544,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"又一間米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d5fe996d96a0e86ab77f30979c70895fbe2235","tid":625544,"uid":810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"廣告文 不了"},{"pid":"dc39d2179eae973d794b627bb48f8b4a9866234e","tid":625544,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pi